    NavLogo, 
    MobileIcon, 
    NavMenu, 
    NavItem,

    NavBtn,
    NavBtnLink
} from './NavbarElements';


const Navbar = () => {
    return (

                </NavbarContainer>
            </Nav>
        </>
    )
}

export default Navbar
